title: EastEnders legend set to make a shock return to soap?
text:
Denise Fox has been struggling ever since she gave her son up for adoption. 
Her stress from her huge decision started to impact her work life, as she had a huge bust up with Minute Mart owner Patrick Truman. 
She had spoken about the state of the shop to a local newspaper, and her move did not go down well with him at all. 
BBC ESTRANGED WIFE: Yolande moved away after she split from Patrick years ago Sexiest soap stars Tuesday, 14th February 2017 Check out our gallery on the sexiest soap stars of our time, from Brooke Vincent to Jennifer Metcalfe 1 / 95 
Denise was then told by Patrick that she was to have a meeting at the Minute Mart head office. 
He also confirmed that his ex-wife Yolande would be in the meeting to discuss what happens next for her. 
Does this mean that she will be making a permanent return to the soap?
